Package: katex
Type: Package
Title: Rendering Math to HTML and MathML in R
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("Jeroen", "Ooms", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "jeroen@berkeley.edu",
    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4035-0289"))
Description: Convert latex math expressions to HTML for use in markdown documents
    or package manual pages. The rendering is done in R using the V8 engine (i.e.
    server-side), which eliminates the need for embedding the 'MathJax' library 
    in the output web pages.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://docs.ropensci.org/katex/,
    https://github.com/ropensci/katex
    https://katex.org/docs/options.html (upstream)
BugReports: https://github.com/ropensci/katex/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
Imports: V8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
